1
00:01:45,150 --> 00:01:47,400
I, Fan Pengju, have returned!

2
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:51,560
He's back! He's back! He's back!

3
00:01:52,400 --> 00:01:53,120
Fan Pengju.

4
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:55,560
Don't... don't be so arrogant.

5
00:01:55,560 --> 00:01:58,040
You're back, fine, you're back.

6
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,840
But... but you brought so many bandits.

7
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:03,350
Don't open your mouth just to spout nonsense.

8
00:02:03,870 --> 00:02:04,870
Up until now,

9
00:02:05,350 --> 00:02:06,350
have I touched you at all?

10
00:02:07,150 --> 00:02:08,120
Have you ever seen

11
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:10,120
such reasonable bandits?

12
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:13,200
You just haven't started robbing us yet.

13
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,280
You made such a big scene.

14
00:02:15,520 --> 00:02:17,000
Is it just for show?

15
00:02:18,840 --> 00:02:21,310
It's to tell you clearly

16
00:02:21,710 --> 00:02:24,190
who calls the shots now.

17
00:02:27,240 --> 00:02:28,080
Elders,

18
00:02:28,470 --> 00:02:29,870
Simpleton didn't collude with bandits before,

19
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,240
and he isn't a bandit now.

20
00:02:31,590 --> 00:02:33,430
They are the Brotherhood, who are above the law.

21
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,590
They surely won't do anything to harm everyone.

22
00:02:36,240 --> 00:02:36,840
Yu Zhen.

23
00:02:37,400 --> 00:02:38,280
These few here...

24
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:42,120
ganged up to bury me alive.

25
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,710
I'm the bigger man,

26
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:45,910
so I won't hold it against them.

27
00:02:46,150 --> 00:02:47,030
On the contrary,

28
00:02:47,710 --> 00:02:49,400
I've come to protect you.

29
00:02:50,120 --> 00:02:50,840
You?

30
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,960
Protect us how?

31
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:53,840
If you don't cry "stop thief" while being the thief,

32
00:02:54,080 --> 00:02:57,120
or steal from your own, that's good enough.

33
00:02:57,470 --> 00:02:58,960
I won't rob you.

34
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:01,910
There are plenty of people who want to rob you.

35
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:05,240
As long as you provide some money and grain regularly,

36
00:03:05,630 --> 00:03:08,080
I will keep you safe.

37
00:03:09,150 --> 00:03:10,430
To put it plainly,

38
00:03:10,710 --> 00:03:12,750
you just want to take money

39
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,400
out of us common folks' pockets.

40
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:14,960
Wrong.

41
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:19,360
The common folks are suffering right now.

42
00:03:19,590 --> 00:03:21,800
Even bandits feel bad robbing them.

43
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,280
What do they want to rob?

44
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:29,280
They want to rob you lot who are fat with wealth.

45
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,560
You're the shrewd one.

46
00:03:31,870 --> 00:03:33,960
You want both fame and fortune.

47
00:03:34,310 --> 00:03:38,030
I'm taking your money to ward off disaster for you.

48
00:03:38,030 --> 00:03:40,750
This... this probably isn't up to you.

49
00:03:41,430 --> 00:03:43,120
We have the local militia.

50
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:44,520
Your local militia?

51
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,470
Do they have as many men as I do?

52
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,430
Do they have as many guns as I do?

53
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:57,120
Old Master! Old Master! Old Master!

54
00:03:57,870 --> 00:04:00,960
Why are you shouting in such a panic?

55
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,680
The Young Master is back!

56
00:04:02,750 --> 00:04:04,150
The Young Master is back!

57
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,360
Are you dreaming?

58
00:04:08,310 --> 00:04:09,080
Now,

59
00:04:09,430 --> 00:04:10,910
I can't hide it from you anymore.

60
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:12,400
To tell you the truth,

61
00:04:13,150 --> 00:04:15,520
the Young Master never died.

62
00:04:16,030 --> 00:04:17,470
I knew from the very beginning

63
00:04:17,590 --> 00:04:19,150
that he was alive all along.

64
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,720
Whose kid is this?

65
00:04:31,870 --> 00:04:33,120
He looks quite sturdy.

66
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,510
I'm from the Qian family.

67
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,000
What are you doing?

68
00:04:36,510 --> 00:04:37,160
What?

69
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,000
Is the lollipop tasty?

70
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:42,680
It's tasty.

71
00:04:42,830 --> 00:04:44,240
Tell your grandpa to give some money

72
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:46,160
for those other kids

73
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,000
to buy some too, okay?

74
00:04:48,070 --> 00:04:49,830
Okay. We have money at home.

75
00:04:50,950 --> 00:04:51,680
See that?

76
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:53,240
Even the kid is so sensible.

77
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:56,190
As a grandpa, set an example.

78
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,560
And the rest of you,

79
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,160
hand it over.

80
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:04,390
Set an example too.

81
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,360
Come on, hurry up.

82
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:07,270
Take it out.

83
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:11,000
Are you dismissing a beggar?

84
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:12,480
This is money to save your lives.

85
00:05:12,480 --> 00:05:13,070
Yes.

86
00:05:13,070 --> 00:05:14,510
I... I didn't bring enough money today.

87
00:05:14,510 --> 00:05:15,750
I... I'll go back and get it later.

88
00:05:30,310 --> 00:05:31,430
Make way, make way, make way

89
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:32,390
Hurry, make way, make way

90
00:05:32,510 --> 00:05:33,480
Make way, make way

91
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,160
Granduncle

92
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:38,390
Granduncle

93
00:05:38,630 --> 00:05:40,160
Granduncle

94
00:05:40,160 --> 00:05:40,920
Stand up

95
00:05:42,830 --> 00:05:43,510
Kneel down

96
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:47,870
You unfilial son

97
00:05:48,190 --> 00:05:50,560
Buried alive for colluding with bandits, yet unrepentant

98
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:53,190
Now you've gone and become a bandit yourself

99
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:55,000
I am not a bandit

100
00:05:55,240 --> 00:05:56,510
In front of so many people

101
00:05:56,510 --> 00:05:58,000
You kidnapped someone's child

102
00:05:58,600 --> 00:06:01,720
How is that any different from what bandits do?

103
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,430
It is even worse than them

104
00:06:04,240 --> 00:06:06,480
I did it to help more children

105
00:06:06,870 --> 00:06:08,160
You think you're the King of Heaven?

106
00:06:11,190 --> 00:06:12,160
What is it?

107
00:06:16,190 --> 00:06:17,680
In front of all these people

108
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,750
I still need to save face

109
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:23,430
You think it's like before?

110
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:25,000
You can hit me whenever you want?

111
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:28,000
You... your wings have hardened

112
00:06:28,920 --> 00:06:31,000
I am working on the redistribution of wealth

113
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,070
You wouldn't understand

114
00:06:32,310 --> 00:06:34,160
Every family's property

115
00:06:34,750 --> 00:06:37,310
Isn't it accumulated by generations of ancestors

116
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:39,680
Through hard labor?

117
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:42,600
It doesn't just fall from the sky

118
00:06:43,950 --> 00:06:46,870
You've read too many books at home

119
00:06:47,310 --> 00:06:49,360
What is happening out there

120
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:51,070
You don't understand at all

121
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:54,310
For the poor to turn their lives around now

122
00:06:54,390 --> 00:06:55,870
It is basically impossible

123
00:06:56,270 --> 00:06:57,430
Do a little business

124
00:06:58,190 --> 00:07:00,000
And get exploited by local ruffians

125
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:02,000
If the business gets big

126
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:04,390
The government loots you

127
00:07:06,510 --> 00:07:08,240
These... my brothers here

128
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:13,160
Only went up the mountain because they were too poor and miserable

129
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:17,920
Then what about these old masters?

130
00:07:18,190 --> 00:07:19,630
How did they offend you?

131
00:07:20,270 --> 00:07:21,240
They have a lot of money

132
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:23,310
Take it out for everyone to use

133
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,830
Use it together?

134
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,240
A disgrace to the Fan family

135
00:07:27,950 --> 00:07:29,000
I failed to teach you properly

136
00:07:29,830 --> 00:07:31,120
I have failed everyone

137
00:07:32,270 --> 00:07:34,240
Disband your men immediately

138
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:36,120
And come back with me

139
00:07:37,190 --> 00:07:39,000
I will give everyone an explanation

140
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,120
Explain what? What explanation?

141
00:07:42,190 --> 00:07:43,190
Since I was little

142
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,480
You've always controlled me

143
00:07:46,190 --> 00:07:47,630
You never supported me

144
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:48,800
Now I...

145
00:07:49,750 --> 00:07:51,830
Have brothers and guns

146
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:53,560
I want to call the shots myself

147
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:55,630
You call the shots?

148
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,000
If you don't go back today

149
00:07:58,870 --> 00:08:01,480
Then don't ever go back in this lifetime

150
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,600
I didn't want to go back anyway

151
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:07,870
You...

152
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:22,920
Young Master, what are you doing?

153
00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:25,630
Simpleton!

154
00:08:28,070 --> 00:08:28,750
Simpleton!

155
00:08:29,870 --> 00:08:30,920
Old Master! Old Master!

156
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:31,560
Granduncle.

157
00:08:31,630 --> 00:08:32,360
Old Master!

158
00:08:35,830 --> 00:08:37,360
To produce such a disgrace...

159
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:39,120
And even set up a spirit tablet for him!

160
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:43,600
I... Even if the Fan family line ends with me...

161
00:08:43,870 --> 00:08:45,750
I will strike his name from the genealogy!

162
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:47,840
Go to hell!

163
00:08:48,390 --> 00:08:48,870
Old Master!

164
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:49,870
Easy, easy, Old Master.

165
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:51,320
Easy, easy, Old Master.

166
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:52,720
Old Master! Old Master! Old Master!

167
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:55,200
Help! The Old Master has fainted!

168
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:56,960
Quick, someone come! Help!

169
00:08:57,870 --> 00:08:59,000
Rich folks, halt!

170
00:09:00,790 --> 00:09:01,630
Pay up.

171
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,000
Toll fee.

172
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,840
Search, search, search.

173
00:09:04,670 --> 00:09:05,480
What are you hiding from?

174
00:09:06,790 --> 00:09:08,150
What on earth is this?

175
00:09:08,840 --> 00:09:09,480
Halt!

176
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,790
Got any grain at home?

177
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:13,320
Got any money?

178
00:09:13,910 --> 00:09:14,600
Grain.

179
00:09:14,790 --> 00:09:15,440
Not bad.

180
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:17,120
Take this.

181
00:09:17,120 --> 00:09:18,120
This is for you.

182
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:18,750
Go.

183
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:19,320
Thank you!

184
00:09:19,320 --> 00:09:20,000
Go, go, go.

185
00:09:20,510 --> 00:09:21,080
Open the gate!

186
00:09:21,630 --> 00:09:22,670
Come, Yu Zhen.

187
00:09:24,240 --> 00:09:25,150
You have a bowl too.

188
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:27,600
Are you trying to anger Granduncle to death?

189
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:30,150
I can't reason with him.

190
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:32,240
The things I'm doing now...

191
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,790
He just doesn't understand.

192
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,440
Isn't that clearly...

193
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,870
Cutting ties with him?

194
00:09:38,150 --> 00:09:39,600
Those old fogies...

195
00:09:39,870 --> 00:09:41,960
Never looked me in the eye once.

196
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,870
You don't want your man...

197
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:45,630
To never amount to anything.

198
00:09:47,150 --> 00:09:48,080
You have to support me.

199
00:09:49,270 --> 00:09:50,000
Brother Fan.

200
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,240
I support you.

201
00:09:53,510 --> 00:09:54,720
But you really shouldn't have used the child.

202
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:56,720
Brother Fan would never hurt a child.

203
00:09:59,390 --> 00:10:00,550
Eat up.

204
00:10:00,670 --> 00:10:01,600
It's not poisoned.

205
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,080
Eat up.

206
00:10:03,750 --> 00:10:05,240
If you don't eat, I'll beat you!

207
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,720
You're so used to being a bandit...

208
00:10:08,030 --> 00:10:09,670
You've forgotten how to be a good person?

209
00:10:10,600 --> 00:10:11,150
Let me do it.

210
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,390
Sister Yu Zhen.

211
00:10:14,750 --> 00:10:16,030
Brother Fan definitely wouldn't...

212
00:10:16,480 --> 00:10:17,840
Do anything wicked.

213
00:10:17,960 --> 00:10:20,080
Sometimes extreme measures are normal.

214
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:22,080
It's the Jianghu, unavoidable.

215
00:10:23,320 --> 00:10:25,080
You just need to trust Brother Fan.

216
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,080
Supporting him is the right thing to do.

217
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,440
Are we good people?

218
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:42,630
See that?

219
00:10:43,200 --> 00:10:43,960
Keep feeding him.

220
00:10:44,390 --> 00:10:44,960
Come on.

221
00:10:47,630 --> 00:10:48,390
Eat, come on.

222
00:10:48,390 --> 00:10:50,120
Come eat. Good boy.

223
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:55,510
Men at birth...

224
00:10:55,630 --> 00:11:00,440
Are naturally good.

225
00:11:01,480 --> 00:11:02,630
I'll write it down.

226
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,080
You must remember this.

227
00:11:04,360 --> 00:11:05,320
Okay.

228
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:26,910
Right.

229
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:28,910
Come on! Come on! Come on!

230
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:30,870
Harder! Harder!

231
00:11:32,510 --> 00:11:34,480
Okay, good, good, good. Come on.

232
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,030
That's enough. That's enough.

233
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:46,870
That chubby little brother who looked after you before...

234
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,840
You really couldn't find him?

235
00:11:49,270 --> 00:11:50,030
We couldn't.

236
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:51,870
We looked everywhere we could.

237
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,120
Don't move!

238
00:11:59,510 --> 00:12:00,510
What are you all doing?

239
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:02,550
I'm teaching you to read.

240
00:12:02,960 --> 00:12:04,440
I'm teaching them combat.

241
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,600
Learning this stuff at such a young age?

242
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,510
Reading is useful.

243
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,790
Learning this is more useful.

244
00:12:12,200 --> 00:12:13,510
In this day and age...

245
00:12:14,320 --> 00:12:16,270
I want to teach them from a young age...

246
00:12:16,750 --> 00:12:17,910
...how to protect themselves.

247
00:12:19,870 --> 00:12:22,150
I want to learn this! I don't want to study!

248
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:23,630
When you grow up...

249
00:12:24,240 --> 00:12:25,270
...do you all want to become bandits?

250
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,320
If we can be as dashing as Big Brother Fan...

251
00:12:27,390 --> 00:12:28,510
...then I want to be a bandit too!

252
00:12:28,510 --> 00:12:29,390
When I grow up...

253
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:31,840
...I want to roam the Jianghu with Big Brother Fan.

254
00:12:32,320 --> 00:12:33,270
Good, good, good.

255
00:12:33,720 --> 00:12:35,440
But let me make one thing clear.

256
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,550
We are not bandits.

257
00:12:37,720 --> 00:12:40,440
We are the Brotherhood that robs the rich to aid the poor.

258
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,150
It's all the same!

259
00:12:41,360 --> 00:12:42,000
It's all the same!

260
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,550
We just want to follow Big Brother Fan!

261
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,000
I want to follow Big Brother Fan too!

262
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:46,750
Alright, alright, follow me.

263
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:48,480
Go out and practice.

264
00:12:56,030 --> 00:12:57,630
The little ones just think it's fun.

265
00:12:58,150 --> 00:12:59,320
Don't take it to heart.

266
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:02,080
Learning these things so young...

267
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:03,550
...is it really useful?

268
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:05,390
Sister Yu Zhen.

269
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,510
Not every child...

270
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:10,270
...has someone to care for and look after them.

271
00:13:11,390 --> 00:13:12,360
And certainly not every child...

272
00:13:12,360 --> 00:13:13,790
...is as lucky as you are.

273
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:16,750
To have a father who is a teacher...

274
00:13:17,790 --> 00:13:19,720
...and a man like Big Brother Fan.

275
00:13:21,630 --> 00:13:23,120
They can only rely on themselves.

276
00:13:24,630 --> 00:13:26,000
Only by learning these things...

277
00:13:26,150 --> 00:13:27,870
...can they take good care of themselves...

278
00:13:28,960 --> 00:13:30,240
...and not get bullied.

279
00:13:30,720 --> 00:13:31,870
Give us that gun!

280
00:13:31,870 --> 00:13:33,000
Give the gun to me!

281
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,600
Come on, give us the gun!

282
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:36,750
Give us the gun!

283
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:57,510
Doctor Niu, thank you.

284
00:13:57,790 --> 00:13:58,510
You're too kind, too kind.

285
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,360
It's just ahead, not far now.

286
00:14:03,320 --> 00:14:04,080
It's right there.

287
00:14:04,910 --> 00:14:06,390
When I found him...

288
00:14:06,670 --> 00:14:08,320
...he was already stone cold dead.

289
00:14:09,150 --> 00:14:10,550
I've brought you here, so I'll be going now.

290
00:14:10,910 --> 00:14:12,440
Don't say I brought you here.

291
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,670
And definitely don't say you know me.

292
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,510
You...

293
00:14:16,670 --> 00:14:18,390
...even though you treat cows...

294
00:14:18,670 --> 00:14:19,360
...but...

295
00:14:19,840 --> 00:14:20,910
...you cured me.

296
00:14:21,390 --> 00:14:22,750
You're my lifesaver.

297
00:14:22,910 --> 00:14:23,630
And now...

298
00:14:24,320 --> 00:14:26,630
...you've buried Xiu Gu's father.

299
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,750
I must reward you handsomely.

300
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:29,960
No, no, no.

301
00:14:30,600 --> 00:14:31,870
No need, no need, no need.

302
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:33,960
If... if...

303
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:35,840
I'll be stuck in this mess like a cat in sticky rice.

304
00:14:35,960 --> 00:14:37,240
They'll say I'm colluding with bandits.

305
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:40,440
If I tell you to take it, just take it!

306
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:41,390
Seriously...

307
00:14:41,750 --> 00:14:42,960
Who dares to run their mouth?

308
00:14:43,390 --> 00:14:44,320
I'll deal with them.

309
00:14:44,440 --> 00:14:45,320
Take it.

310
00:14:49,270 --> 00:14:50,000
You can go now.

311
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:03,910
Lao Dong

312
00:15:05,630 --> 00:15:06,510
You

313
00:15:07,390 --> 00:15:08,390
saved my life.

314
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:12,750
And you died saving Yu Zhen.

315
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,360
Without you, we wouldn't be here.

316
00:15:19,550 --> 00:15:20,360
Your kindness...

317
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,840
we must repay it.

318
00:15:25,000 --> 00:15:26,840
When you were alive...

319
00:15:28,550 --> 00:15:31,270
you worried most about Xiu Gu.

320
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:35,270
You worried about her future marriage.

321
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:39,630
Now she is...

322
00:15:40,630 --> 00:15:43,750
all alone and helpless.

323
00:15:44,550 --> 00:15:46,600
Miserable...

324
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:49,670
and solitary.

325
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:54,910
And Yu Zhen won't say where she stands.

326
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:57,360
Lao Dong...

327
00:15:57,670 --> 00:16:00,480
what am I supposed to do?

328
00:16:01,390 --> 00:16:02,480
I agree.

329
00:16:07,150 --> 00:16:08,630
Lao Dong!

330
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:11,790
Yu Zhen has agreed!

331
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:12,840
Come.

332
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:14,790
The three of us...

333
00:16:15,150 --> 00:16:16,750
will kowtow to Father.

334
00:16:31,630 --> 00:16:32,360
Lao Dong...

335
00:16:33,360 --> 00:16:34,200
for your death...

336
00:16:34,960 --> 00:16:37,150
I will make sure justice is served.

337
00:16:37,630 --> 00:16:38,200
Bad news!

338
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,270
Bad news! Bad news!

339
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,440
Why the panic?

340
00:16:41,510 --> 00:16:42,910
That Fan guy and Xiu Gu...

341
00:16:42,910 --> 00:16:44,120
are here with a bunch of bandits!

342
00:16:46,240 --> 00:16:46,960
We were just looking for him.

343
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,600
Now he's delivered himself to our doorstep.

344
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,790
They brought guns, too!

345
00:16:50,790 --> 00:16:52,720
Young Master, perhaps you should hide for now.

346
00:16:52,790 --> 00:16:53,790
Why should I hide?

347
00:16:54,030 --> 00:16:55,600
Would he dare touch me?

348
00:16:55,720 --> 00:16:57,600
Dong the Drunkard died at our hands.

349
00:16:57,750 --> 00:16:59,030
A desperate dog will jump a wall.

350
00:16:59,840 --> 00:17:01,600
A cornered rabbit will bite.

351
00:17:03,120 --> 00:17:04,790
Go, go notify Regiment Commander Qin.

352
00:17:05,120 --> 00:17:05,510
Yes.

353
00:17:05,840 --> 00:17:06,670
Use the back door.

354
00:17:13,750 --> 00:17:14,550
Come on!

355
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:18,590
Get the weapons!

356
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,550
Don't move! Don't move!

357
00:17:45,030 --> 00:17:46,750
Put them down! Put them down!

358
00:17:51,030 --> 00:17:52,350
Come here! Squat down!

359
00:17:53,350 --> 00:17:54,070
Keep a low profile.

360
00:17:54,750 --> 00:17:55,680
Don't shoot.

361
00:17:58,070 --> 00:17:59,200
Tell Huo to come out!

362
00:17:59,310 --> 00:18:00,240
How dare you!

363
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:01,880
Our Young Master...

364
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:03,960
isn't someone you can see just because you want to.

365
00:18:10,270 --> 00:18:10,790
Search the place!

366
00:18:11,110 --> 00:18:11,720
Yes!

367
00:18:18,720 --> 00:18:20,270
I won't make things hard for the servants.

368
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:22,640
Every debt has its debtor.

369
00:18:23,310 --> 00:18:25,920
I'm only after the ringleader who bullies people.

370
00:18:26,160 --> 00:18:27,590
You smug villain.

371
00:18:27,880 --> 00:18:29,920
This isn't a place for you to throw your weight around.

372
00:18:45,110 --> 00:18:46,270
Boss, no one's here.

373
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:47,960
He must have run away.

374
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:51,640
So Huo abandoned you lot?

375
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:54,440
I hate disloyal people like that.

376
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:56,510
What a joke.

377
00:18:57,350 --> 00:19:00,070
Our Young Master knows when to yield to circumstances.

378
00:19:00,510 --> 00:19:03,310
A life for a life.

379
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:07,550
Then come at me.

380
00:19:18,790 --> 00:19:20,310
I was the one who tied you up.

381
00:19:21,310 --> 00:19:22,720
Young Mistress Fan...

382
00:19:23,200 --> 00:19:24,590
was also detained by me.

383
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:27,550
And your old man...

384
00:19:28,350 --> 00:19:29,720
was killed by me.

385
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:34,350
It has nothing to do with our Young Master.

386
00:19:35,480 --> 00:19:37,550
The Huo family has shown me kindness for two generations.

387
00:19:38,200 --> 00:19:39,070
This life...

388
00:19:40,790 --> 00:19:41,510
I will pay with it.

389
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:53,480
Do it, then.

390
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:00,790
Since you're a man of honor...

391
00:20:02,270 --> 00:20:03,720
I'll grant your wish.

392
00:20:04,510 --> 00:20:06,070
I'll send you on your way.

393
00:20:57,960 --> 00:20:58,590
Brothers

394
00:20:59,510 --> 00:21:00,270
Hurry up, let's go

395
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:02,640
The soldiers will be chasing us soon

396
00:21:02,720 --> 00:21:03,830
Xiu Gu, take this one

397
00:21:05,830 --> 00:21:07,350
Young Master Huo is the real culprit

398
00:21:07,480 --> 00:21:08,400
I don't need you to remind me

399
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:09,920
I won't let him off either

400
00:21:10,640 --> 00:21:11,270
Let's go

401
00:21:13,590 --> 00:21:14,480
Yu Zhen, sit here

402
00:21:14,830 --> 00:21:15,590
I don't want to sit

403
00:21:18,200 --> 00:21:19,240
Then I'll walk with you

404
00:21:22,310 --> 00:21:23,200
What's wrong with you?

405
00:21:28,030 --> 00:21:28,590
Simpleton

406
00:21:30,030 --> 00:21:30,750
I feel like

407
00:21:31,790 --> 00:21:33,000
I barely recognize you anymore

408
00:21:33,920 --> 00:21:35,830
I don't even recognize myself

409
00:21:36,550 --> 00:21:37,400
Lately

410
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,240
I've changed so fast

411
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:41,680
All these things

412
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:44,070
it's like I was born knowing them

413
00:21:44,510 --> 00:21:45,400
I didn't even have to learn

414
00:21:45,750 --> 00:21:48,070
It all comes so naturally to me

415
00:21:49,310 --> 00:21:50,960
You mean killing and arson?

416
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:52,310
Does that come naturally to you?

417
00:21:54,070 --> 00:21:56,640
I meant upholding justice

418
00:21:57,240 --> 00:21:59,480
You actually think you're doing good deeds?

419
00:22:04,440 --> 00:22:07,110
You've been so sarcastic lately

420
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:08,960
What's the matter?

421
00:22:16,310 --> 00:22:17,880
You are not my Simpleton anymore

422
00:22:19,070 --> 00:22:20,310
I'm not your Simpleton

423
00:22:20,830 --> 00:22:22,270
then whose Simpleton am I?

424
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,440
I used to think

425
00:22:27,310 --> 00:22:28,480
it was just my lack of experience

426
00:22:29,240 --> 00:22:31,160
not understanding the dangers of your Jianghu

427
00:22:34,350 --> 00:22:35,310
But my Simpleton

428
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,310
wouldn't be so cruel to Granduncle

429
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:39,550
beating people on a whim

430
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:42,310
nor would he teach children to be delinquents

431
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:44,240
"I'm here to send you on your way"

432
00:22:45,030 --> 00:22:46,510
nor would he take a life

433
00:22:47,240 --> 00:22:48,550
or burn down people's houses

434
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:51,400
In your eyes

435
00:22:51,960 --> 00:22:53,070
am I really that bad?

436
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:56,270
Didn't you see the good things I did?

437
00:22:58,480 --> 00:23:00,680
I adopted those homeless children

438
00:23:01,030 --> 00:23:02,160
I repay kindness with kindness

439
00:23:02,590 --> 00:23:04,440
Did you not see any of that?

440
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,640
But you can't lose your conscience

441
00:23:06,720 --> 00:23:08,240
and become so ruthless

442
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:10,270
You didn't see how they treated me

443
00:23:11,590 --> 00:23:12,750
If you don't believe me, ask Xiu Gu

444
00:23:14,920 --> 00:23:15,960
Why can't you be like

445
00:23:16,160 --> 00:23:18,240
Xiu Gu and support me?

446
00:23:19,440 --> 00:23:20,720
I haven't been like Xiu Gu

447
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:21,880
going through so much with you

448
00:23:22,830 --> 00:23:23,790
But I also don't think

449
00:23:24,000 --> 00:23:25,310
that what Xiu Gu does is for your own good

450
00:23:29,200 --> 00:23:30,070
What?

451
00:23:31,590 --> 00:23:32,160
Big Brother

452
00:23:32,400 --> 00:23:33,880
I wasn't eavesdropping

453
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:34,880
I was guarding the rear

454
00:23:35,160 --> 00:23:35,680
Look

455
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:37,270
they've gone far ahead

456
00:23:37,270 --> 00:23:38,350
You two didn't catch up

457
00:23:38,720 --> 00:23:39,640
As your armed guard

458
00:23:39,640 --> 00:23:40,880
I have to protect you closely

459
00:23:42,480 --> 00:23:43,070
Go, go, go

460
00:23:44,790 --> 00:23:45,510
You two keep arguing

461
00:23:45,590 --> 00:23:46,510
I'll wait for you over there

462
00:23:58,510 --> 00:23:59,160
Simpleton

463
00:24:01,440 --> 00:24:02,720
come back with me

464
00:24:03,920 --> 00:24:04,920
I can't go back

465
00:24:05,350 --> 00:24:06,510
And I don't want to go back

466
00:24:07,310 --> 00:24:08,960
Then let's find a small town to settle down

467
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:11,400
Live a quiet, peaceful life

468
00:24:12,030 --> 00:24:12,680
Okay?

469
00:24:14,030 --> 00:24:15,480
My ambition

470
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:17,400
is to roam the Jianghu

471
00:24:17,920 --> 00:24:19,590
Now that so many brothers follow me

472
00:24:20,640 --> 00:24:22,070
and they do it willingly

473
00:24:23,310 --> 00:24:25,550
It wasn't easy to get where I am

474
00:24:26,550 --> 00:24:27,550
I want to achieve things

475
00:24:27,920 --> 00:24:29,400
I want to do big things

476
00:24:34,160 --> 00:24:35,000
You just

477
00:24:35,590 --> 00:24:36,680
can't accept it yet

478
00:24:39,960 --> 00:24:40,960
There's still plenty of time

479
00:24:42,750 --> 00:24:43,510
Slowly

480
00:24:46,750 --> 00:24:47,790
you will understand me

481
00:25:08,030 --> 00:25:09,440
Division Commander Chen

482
00:25:10,960 --> 00:25:11,960
Division Commander Chen

483
00:25:12,640 --> 00:25:13,240
What is it?

484
00:25:13,510 --> 00:25:14,480
Division Commander Chen

485
00:25:15,350 --> 00:25:17,440
Division Commander Chen! Help me! Division Commander Chen!

486
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,000
Why is it you again?

487
00:25:19,110 --> 00:25:20,160
It's the bandits!

488
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:22,680
Those bandits are trying to wipe me out!

489
00:25:22,680 --> 00:25:24,070
Did you step on a bandit's tail?

490
00:25:24,720 --> 00:25:25,720
For them to target you everywhere?

491
00:25:25,880 --> 00:25:27,400
Before, because of the cargo matter,

492
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:30,110
I asked you, Division Commander Chen, to help suppress the bandits, right?

493
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:32,160
Who knew they were so cunning?

494
00:25:32,160 --> 00:25:33,510
They managed to get away.

495
00:25:34,160 --> 00:25:34,790
So...

496
00:25:35,440 --> 00:25:37,400
Now they've come to take revenge on me.

497
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:41,030
Why is the version I heard different?

498
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,880
That girl's father...

499
00:25:43,920 --> 00:25:45,400
Seems to have died at your hands.

500
00:25:47,160 --> 00:25:47,750
He...

501
00:25:48,110 --> 00:25:50,350
That was my butler, a momentary slip-up.

502
00:25:51,110 --> 00:25:51,830
Besides...

503
00:25:52,510 --> 00:25:53,830
He was colluding with bandits!

504
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:55,790
He deserved to die!

505
00:25:56,750 --> 00:25:58,440
Then what did you run here for?

506
00:26:01,440 --> 00:26:02,070
Division Commander Chen.

507
00:26:02,510 --> 00:26:03,400
I've decided.

508
00:26:03,790 --> 00:26:05,110
I want to give up business and join the army.

509
00:26:05,830 --> 00:26:07,640
Nowadays bandits are rampant.

510
00:26:07,830 --> 00:26:09,310
I wish to serve under your banner, Division Commander Chen.

511
00:26:09,790 --> 00:26:11,550
To help you suppress the bandits.

512
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,510
You want to join the barracks?

513
00:26:14,070 --> 00:26:15,310
Go report to the recruitment office.

514
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,000
You're joking, Division Commander Chen.

515
00:26:19,550 --> 00:26:20,720
I am a scholar.

516
00:26:21,270 --> 00:26:22,960
I'm afraid I can't carry a gun.

517
00:26:29,680 --> 00:26:30,240
Division Commander Chen.

518
00:26:30,480 --> 00:26:31,880
This is my entire fortune.

519
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:34,480
I hand it to you to expand your armaments.

520
00:26:45,480 --> 00:26:47,240
If you don't mind, Commander...

521
00:26:48,030 --> 00:26:49,160
Let me see.

522
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,750
Move Two to Six.

523
00:27:15,200 --> 00:27:16,590
Remove Four and Eight.

524
00:27:28,550 --> 00:27:29,920
Sacrifice a piece to take the lead.

525
00:27:31,270 --> 00:27:32,350
That's interesting.

526
00:27:32,920 --> 00:27:33,590
Commander.

527
00:27:34,350 --> 00:27:36,310
This game of black and white pieces...

528
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:38,640
Is just like two armies facing off.

529
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:41,880
I, Huo, have read a few books on military strategy.

530
00:27:42,510 --> 00:27:44,640
I know well that Zhuge Liang's brilliant plans...

531
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,680
Can defeat a million mighty soldiers.

532
00:27:47,000 --> 00:27:48,270
No matter how fierce Lu Bu was...

533
00:27:48,790 --> 00:27:50,590
He still met his end at White Gate Tower.

534
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:55,240
You could let me try being a Staff Officer.

535
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:57,000
Thank you, Commander.

536
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,030
From now on...

537
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:00,270
I am a piece on your chessboard, Commander.

538
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:01,240
Wherever you point...

539
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,070
I will strike there.

540
00:28:02,160 --> 00:28:03,680
To offer advice and strategy for you...

541
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:04,830
I will not hesitate.

542
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:16,790
Staff Officer Huo.

543
00:28:17,440 --> 00:28:18,000
Please.

544
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:20,920
Thank you, thank you.

545
00:28:23,030 --> 00:28:24,200
That I have this day...

546
00:28:24,200 --> 00:28:26,790
Is entirely due to the trust of my brothers.

547
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:29,920
Is entirely because you brothers backed me up.

548
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:32,830
Drink more wine.

549
00:28:32,830 --> 00:28:34,830
We'll eat meat in a bit.

550
00:28:34,830 --> 00:28:36,510
Alright!

551
00:28:36,510 --> 00:28:38,400
Cheers!

552
00:28:38,590 --> 00:28:39,200
Brother Fan

553
00:28:39,440 --> 00:28:40,400
To be honest,

554
00:28:40,590 --> 00:28:41,880
I really don't see

555
00:28:41,960 --> 00:28:42,960
what charm you have

556
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:44,510
to win over two women.

557
00:28:45,000 --> 00:28:46,270
You wouldn't understand that.

558
00:28:46,590 --> 00:28:47,920
A woman's perspective and a man's

559
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:48,920
are different.

560
00:28:49,070 --> 00:28:49,880
Women can see things

561
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:51,160
that we men cannot.

562
00:28:52,750 --> 00:28:53,720
My wife...

563
00:28:54,270 --> 00:28:55,640
saw I was the chosen one.

564
00:28:55,830 --> 00:28:57,110
As for Xiu Gu,

565
00:28:57,880 --> 00:28:59,550
sometimes she's like a brother,

566
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:01,270
sometimes like a sister.

567
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:03,200
Anyway, it's different.

568
00:29:03,400 --> 00:29:04,790
Different is good.

569
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:06,750
If they were the same, why get two?

570
00:29:08,110 --> 00:29:09,110
Most importantly,

571
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:10,640
how did you convince the first wife

572
00:29:10,640 --> 00:29:12,110
to let you take a second one?

573
00:29:12,400 --> 00:29:14,110
I'm just lucky.

574
00:29:14,510 --> 00:29:16,270
I found one who is understanding,

575
00:29:16,480 --> 00:29:18,030
and then found another understanding one.

576
00:29:20,200 --> 00:29:21,510
I wonder when we

577
00:29:21,510 --> 00:29:22,790
will have such good fortune.

578
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:24,310
You will, you will. Always.

579
00:29:24,310 --> 00:29:26,030
Everyone will have this good fortune.

580
00:29:26,110 --> 00:29:27,400
Come on.

581
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:30,790
Cheers! Cheers!

582
00:29:47,030 --> 00:29:48,830
I live at the Yangtze's source,

583
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:52,720
and you at the Yangtze's end.

584
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:56,750
Day after day I think of you but cannot see you,

585
00:29:58,310 --> 00:30:00,350
though we drink from the same river.

586
00:30:02,680 --> 00:30:04,750
When will this water cease to flow?

587
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:08,830
When will this sorrow end?

588
00:30:10,110 --> 00:30:12,400
I only wish your heart is like mine,

589
00:30:14,440 --> 00:30:17,510
and never betrays my longing.

590
00:30:27,790 --> 00:30:29,200
They are all drinking.

591
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:33,160
I came to watch the sunset with you.

592
00:30:45,000 --> 00:30:45,830
Yu Zhen.

593
00:30:46,590 --> 00:30:49,070
They say you have the air of a matriarch.

594
00:30:55,590 --> 00:30:56,510
Simpleton.

595
00:30:57,510 --> 00:30:58,310
I'm leaving.

596
00:31:00,960 --> 00:31:03,440
I married Fan Pengju,

597
00:31:04,550 --> 00:31:05,750
not a bandit chief.

598
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:10,270
Although you keep denying you're a bandit,

599
00:31:11,640 --> 00:31:12,790
in the eyes of the world,

600
00:31:13,270 --> 00:31:14,160
there is no difference.

601
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,510
You have your lofty ambitions,

602
00:31:18,510 --> 00:31:20,310
and I have principles I stick to.

603
00:31:21,640 --> 00:31:22,400
I know

604
00:31:23,550 --> 00:31:24,880
you are sincere to me.

605
00:31:26,750 --> 00:31:27,640
And I, to you,

606
00:31:28,880 --> 00:31:30,000
am also sincere.

607
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:33,270
But I can't be like you,

608
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:36,160
nor can I stop you.

609
00:31:37,510 --> 00:31:39,310
We walk different paths.

610
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,070
I don't want to make things hard for you.

611
00:31:44,000 --> 00:31:44,720
Do not worry about me.

612
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:46,400
Yu Zhen
